dct_title_s: Southern Morocco 1:125,000. Amizmiz, sheet 18. A.M.S. P632
dct_description_sm: AMS 1. Alternate title: No. 18 Amizmiz. Polyconic projection. Northwest Africa zone grid. Relief shown by 100 foot contour intervals. Compiled from Service Geographique du Maroc 1:100,000, 1928 to 1939. Road classifications corrected from Army Map road map Northwest Africa, 1:1,000,000, 1942.
dct_publisher_sm: Washington, D.C. : Army Map Service, U.S. Army, 1943.
